#. <section class="sutta" id="an5.34"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an5.34:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 5"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 5"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.34:0.2"
msgid "4. Sumanavagga"
msgstr "4. With Sumanā"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an5.34:0.3"
msgid "34. Sīhasenāpatisutta"
msgstr "34. With General Sīha"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli3.39"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an5.34:1.1"
msgid "Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā vesāliyaṃ viharati mahāvane kūṭāgārasālāyaṃ."
msgstr ""
"At one time the Buddha was staying near Vesālī, at the Great Wood, in the "
"hall with the peaked roof."

msgctxt "an5.34:1.2"
msgid ""
"Atha kho sīho senāpati yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ "
"abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho sīho senāpati "
"bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"Then General Sīha went up to the Buddha, bowed, sat down to one side, and "
"said to him:"

msgctxt "an5.34:1.3"
msgid "“sakkā nu kho, bhante, bhagavā sandiṭṭhikaṃ dānaphalaṃ paññāpetun”ti?"
msgstr ""
"“Sir, can you point out a fruit of giving that’s apparent in the present "
"life?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an5.34:2.1"
msgid "“Sakkā, sīhā”ti bhagavā avoca:"
msgstr "“I can, Sīha,” said the Buddha."

msgctxt "an5.34:2.2"
msgid "“dāyako, sīha, dānapati bahuno janassa piyo hoti manāpo."
msgstr "“A giver, a donor is dear and beloved to many people."

msgctxt "an5.34:2.3"
msgid ""
"Yampi, sīha, dāyako dānapati bahuno janassa piyo hoti manāpo, idampi "
"sandiṭṭhikaṃ dānaphalaṃ."
msgstr "This is a fruit of giving that’s apparent in the present life."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an5.34:3.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, sīha, dāyakaṃ dānapatiṃ santo sappurisā bhajanti."
msgstr "Furthermore, good people associate with a giver."

msgctxt "an5.34:3.2"
msgid ""
"Yampi, sīha, dāyakaṃ dānapatiṃ santo sappurisā bhajanti, idampi sandiṭṭhikaṃ "
"dānaphalaṃ."
msgstr "This is another fruit of giving that’s apparent in the present life."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an5.34:4.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, sīha, dāyakassa dānapatino kalyāṇo kittisaddo abbhuggacchati."
msgstr "Furthermore, a giver gains a good reputation."

msgctxt "an5.34:4.2"
msgid ""
"Yampi, sīha, dāyakassa dānapatino kalyāṇo kittisaddo abbhuggacchati, idampi "
"sandiṭṭhikaṃ dānaphalaṃ."
msgstr "This is another fruit of giving that’s apparent in the present life."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
#. VAR: visārado → visāradova (bj)
msgctxt "an5.34:5.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, sīha, dāyako dānapati yaṃ yadeva parisaṃ upasaṅkamati—yadi "
"khattiyaparisaṃ yadi brāhmaṇaparisaṃ yadi gahapatiparisaṃ yadi samaṇaparisaṃ—"
"visārado upasaṅkamati amaṅkubhūto."
msgstr ""
"Furthermore, a giver enters any kind of assembly bold and assured, whether "
"it’s an assembly of aristocrats, brahmins, householders, or ascetics."

msgctxt "an5.34:5.2"
msgid ""
"Yampi, sīha, dāyako dānapati yaṃ yadeva parisaṃ upasaṅkamati—yadi "
"khattiyaparisaṃ yadi brāhmaṇaparisaṃ yadi gahapatiparisaṃ yadi samaṇaparisaṃ—"
"visārado upasaṅkamati amaṅkubhūto, idampi sandiṭṭhikaṃ dānaphalaṃ."
msgstr "This is another fruit of giving that’s apparent in the present life."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "an5.34:6.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, sīha, dāyako dānapati kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā sugatiṃ "
"saggaṃ lokaṃ upapajjati."
msgstr ""
"Furthermore, when a giver’s body breaks up, after death, they’re reborn in a "
"good place, a heavenly realm."

#. VAR: idaṃ → idaṃpi (s1-3, pts1) | idampi sīha (mr)
msgctxt "an5.34:6.2"
msgid ""
"Yampi, sīha, dāyako dānapati kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā sugatiṃ saggaṃ lokaṃ "
"upapajjati, idaṃ samparāyikaṃ dānaphalan”ti."
msgstr "This is a fruit of giving to do with lives to come.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli3.40"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "an5.34:7.1"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, sīho senāpati bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "When he said this, General Sīha said to the Buddha:"

msgctxt "an5.34:7.2"
msgid ""
"“yānimāni, bhante, bhagavatā cattāri sandiṭṭhikāni dānaphalāni akkhātāni, "
"nāhaṃ ettha bhagavato saddhāya gacchāmi; ahaṃ petāni jānāmi."
msgstr ""
"“When it comes to those four fruits of giving that are apparent in the "
"present life, I don’t have to rely on faith in the Buddha, for I know them "
"too."

msgctxt "an5.34:7.3"
msgid "Ahaṃ, bhante, dāyako dānapati bahuno janassa piyo manāpo."
msgstr "I’m a giver, a donor, and am dear and beloved to many people."

msgctxt "an5.34:7.4"
msgid "Ahaṃ, bhante, dāyako dānapati; maṃ santo sappurisā bhajanti."
msgstr "I’m a giver, and good people associate with me."

msgctxt "an5.34:7.5"
msgid ""
"Ahaṃ, bhante, dāyako dānapati; mayhaṃ kalyāṇo kittisaddo abbhuggato: ‘sīho "
"senāpati dāyako kārako saṅghupaṭṭhāko’ti."
msgstr ""
"I’m a giver, and I have this good reputation: ‘General Sīha gives, serves, "
"and attends on the Saṅgha.’"

msgctxt "an5.34:7.6"
msgid ""
"Ahaṃ, bhante, dāyako dānapati yaṃ yadeva parisaṃ upasaṅkamāmi—yadi "
"khattiyaparisaṃ yadi brāhmaṇaparisaṃ yadi gahapatiparisaṃ yadi samaṇaparisaṃ—"
"visārado upasaṅkamāmi amaṅkubhūto."
msgstr ""
"I’m a giver, and I enter any kind of assembly bold and assured, whether it’s "
"an assembly of aristocrats, brahmins, householders, or ascetics."

msgctxt "an5.34:7.7"
msgid ""
"Yānimāni, bhante, bhagavatā cattāri sandiṭṭhikāni dānaphalāni akkhātāni, "
"nāhaṃ ettha bhagavato saddhāya gacchāmi; ahaṃ petāni jānāmi."
msgstr ""
"When it comes to these four fruits of giving that are apparent in the "
"present life, I don’t have to rely on faith in the Buddha, for I know them "
"too."

msgctxt "an5.34:7.8"
msgid "Yañca kho maṃ, bhante, bhagavā evamāha:"
msgstr "But when the Buddha says:"

msgctxt "an5.34:7.9"
msgid ""
"‘dāyako, sīha, dānapati kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā sugatiṃ saggaṃ lokaṃ "
"upapajjatī’ti, etāhaṃ na jānāmi; ettha ca panāhaṃ bhagavato saddhāya "
"gacchāmī”ti."
msgstr ""
"‘When a giver’s body breaks up, after death, they’re reborn in a good place, "
"a heavenly realm.’ I don’t know this, so I have to rely on faith in the "
"Buddha.”"

msgctxt "an5.34:7.10"
msgid "“Evametaṃ, sīha, evametaṃ, sīha."
msgstr "“That’s so true, Sīha! That’s so true!"

msgctxt "an5.34:7.11"
msgid ""
"Dāyako dānapati kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā sugatiṃ saggaṃ lokaṃ upapajjatīti."
msgstr ""
"When a giver’s body breaks up, after death, they’re reborn in a good place, "
"a heavenly realm."

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
msgctxt "an5.34:8.1"
msgid "Dadaṃ piyo hoti bhajanti naṃ bahū,"
msgstr "Giving, you’re loved and befriended by many people."

#. <br>
#. VAR: yaso ca vaḍḍhati → yasobhivaḍḍhati (bj) | yasassa vaḍḍhati (s1-3, km) | yasaṃ pavaḍḍhati (mr)
msgctxt "an5.34:8.2"
msgid "Kittiñca pappoti yaso ca vaḍḍhati;"
msgstr "You get a good reputation, and your fame grows."

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.34:8.3"
msgid "Amaṅkubhūto parisaṃ vigāhati,"
msgstr "A generous man enters an assembly"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.34:8.4"
msgid "Visārado hoti naro amaccharī."
msgstr "bold and assured."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc9"></a>
msgctxt "an5.34:9.1"
msgid "Tasmā hi dānāni dadanti paṇḍitā,"
msgstr "So an astute person, seeking happiness, would give gifts,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.34:9.2"
msgid "Vineyya maccheramalaṃ sukhesino;"
msgstr "having driven out the stain of stinginess."

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.34:9.3"
msgid "Te dīgharattaṃ tidive patiṭṭhitā,"
msgstr "They live long in the threefold heaven,"

#. <br>
#. VAR: sahabyagatā ramanti te → sahabyataṃ gatā ramanti (bj) | sahabyatā ramanti te (mr)
msgctxt "an5.34:9.4"
msgid "Devānaṃ sahabyagatā ramanti te."
msgstr "enjoying the company of the gods."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc10"></a>
#. VAR: cutā → tato cutā (bj)
msgctxt "an5.34:10.1"
msgid "Katāvakāsā katakusalā ito cutā,"
msgstr "Having taken the opportunity to do good, when they pass from here"

#. <br>
#. VAR: nandanaṃ → nandane (s1-3, km)
msgctxt "an5.34:10.2"
msgid "Sayaṃpabhā anuvicaranti nandanaṃ;"
msgstr "they wander radiant in the Garden of Delight."

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.34:10.3"
msgid "Te tattha nandanti ramanti modare,"
msgstr "There they delight, rejoice, and enjoy themselves,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.34:10.4"
msgid "Samappitā kāmaguṇehi pañcahi;"
msgstr "provided with the five kinds of sensual stimulation."

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.34:10.5"
msgid "Katvāna vākyaṃ asitassa tādino,"
msgstr "Doing what the unattached, the poised one says,"

#. <br>
#. VAR: Ramanti sagge → kamanti sabbe (s1-3, km) | ramanti sumanā (mr)
msgctxt "an5.34:10.6"
msgid "Ramanti sagge sugatassa sāvakā”ti."
msgstr "disciples of the Holy One rejoice in heaven.”"

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an5.34:10.7"
msgid "Catutthaṃ."
msgstr ""
